&lt;li&gt;Identify untapped market opportunities and define the partner recruitment strategy to penetrate them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and own partner programs, including tier structures, discount levels, and deal registration policies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the channel revenue forecast and hold partners accountable to KPIs and pipeline commitments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead Quarterly Business Reviews (QBRs) with top-tier partners to drive alignment on revenue goals and growth initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
