&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail with an aptitude for auditing data, spotting inconsistencies, and ensuring adherence to established guidelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent verbal and written communication skills with a customer-service mindset toward supporting internal sales and account teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic familiarity with Excel (e.g., sorting data, filtering, simple formulas) and CRM/ERP platforms like Salesforce and NetSuite.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
