&lt;p&gt;Your job isn’t just to sell, it’s to become a trusted partner to your accounts, deeply understand their organizational structure and roadmap, and expand our footprint with these accounts from ~15% adoption to 75%+. This role requires exceptional enterprise sales acumen, strategic thinking, and a highly collaborative, cross-functional mindset.&lt;/p&gt;
