&lt;li&gt;Engage and build relationships with senior decision-makers and cross-functional stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive significant expansion revenue by deeply embedding SmartRent’s platform into property operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with internal teams including Product, Customer Success, Solutions Engineering, Finance and Marketing to deliver customized strategies and enterprise-level experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead multi-threaded pursuits across business units and regional portfolios&lt;/li&gt;
