&lt;li&gt;Ability to build trusted relationships with all levels of the organization in addition to C-level and VP-level executives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication, presentation, and executive briefing skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in PropTech, complex SaaS/platform or real estate technology required and IoT is strongly preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly collaborative, thrives in a cross-functional, fast-moving environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Salesforce, Gong, ZoomInfo, and account planning frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong data literacy, able to build and defend business cases, value realization, and ROI&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
