&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Account-based marketing experience a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Base Salary Range: $120,000.00 - $150,000 annually. Actual compensation will depend on experience, skills, and internal equity. This role may also be eligible for bonus, commission, or other variable compensation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

